<div class="yui-content">
<div id="wiki-tab-0-0">
<p><strong>分站编号：</strong>Site-CN-82-γ</p>
<p><strong>分站位置：</strong>河南省洛阳市</p>
<p><strong>现任主管：</strong><span style="text-decoration: line-through;"><span style="color: red">Cold_Heart</span></span> <span style="text-decoration: line-through;"><span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cool-heart" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5325378); return false;">Cool_Heart</a></span></span> <span style="text-decoration: line-through;"><span style="color: red">Greedy_Heart</span></span> <span style="text-decoration: line-through;"><span style="color: red">Windy_Heart</span></span> <span style="text-decoration: line-through;"><span style="color: red">Blue_Heart</span></span></p>
<p><strong>主要职能：</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>负责收容宗教类异常物品。</li>
<li>寻找宗教体系中可能存在的异常组织</li>
<li>负责奇术方面的研究与开发</li>
<li>保护/隐藏主站点§。</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>主要人员：</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cool-heart" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5325378); return false;">Cool_Heart</a></span>：<span style="text-decoration: line-through;">低级研究员</span> <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">站点副主管</span> <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">后勤部部长</span> <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">站点主管</span></li>
<li><span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/piracyessayist-zero" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6119968); return false;">PiracyEssayist Zero</a></span>：高级研究员，有精神病史，主要负责Site-CN-82内的形而上学相关异常，即大多无实体并具有时空/认知/概念/模因类性质的异常。</li>
<li><span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/hansheng" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6216806); return false;">Hansheng</a></span>：中级研究员寒升，现负责辅助高级研究员<span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/piracyessayist-zero" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6119968); return false;">PiracyEssayist Zero</a></span>进行其研究工作<span style="text-decoration: line-through;">和陪疯</span>。前有在街上大喊大叫影响市容的犯罪记录，曾因此被当作精神病人与<span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/piracyessayist-zero" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6119968); return false;">PiracyEssayist Zero</a></span>在一间病房并被其引荐入职。</li>
<li><span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/justaswelljar-pepper" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4301969); return false;">JustAswellJar Pepper</a></span>：Site-CN-99 - “演绎部”临时派遣成员，叙事研究部客座首席研究员，[概念污染屏蔽]后不可知论化。</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>部门：</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>神学分析研究部</li>
<li>异常宗教团体追踪调查部</li>
<li>炼金术研究部</li>
<li>奇术研究部</li>
<li>叙事研究部</li>
<li>愚者图书馆</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>研究项目：</strong></p>
<div style="float: center; border: solid 2px #000; padding: 1px 15px; box-shadow: 0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,.2);">
